T02D2419:36a-1: tsarya drishti aa nu ta phanna tva ta bh'a ba na n'a ma /
T02D2419:36a-3: lta spyod skye med kyi bsgom pa zhes bya ba /
T02D2419:36a-4: bla ma rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2419:36a-5: sems nyid stong pa skye med yin //
T02D2419:36a-6: de nyid ma bcos chos nyid de //
T02D2419:36a-7: de yang dbyer med lta ba rtogs //
T02D2419:36a-8: sgom las ma 'das pa ni smra //
T02D2419:36a-9: zhen med rnal 'byor rang sar spyod //
T02D2419:36a-10: phyogs bcur re med 'bras bu yin //
T02D2419:36a-11: de la mi re chags pa spyad //
T02D2419:36a-12: rang bzhin nyams skyes ngo mtshar che //
T02D2419:36a-13: pa na ha ni smra bar byed //
T02D2419:36b-0: gnyis @36b med ye shes rtogs pa yin //
T02D2419:36b-1: bde chen bdud rtsi bdag gis 'thungs //
T02D2419:36b-2: kunydza na'i breng bas mgul pa brgyan //
T02D2419:36b-3: lo ma'i sham thabs brtan par chings //
T02D2419:36b-4: myos bas nags kyi gseb tu 'khyam //
T02D2419:36b-5: bdag nyid pa na ha ngo mtshar mthong //
T02D2419:36b-6: pu ri ma lar bdag po lnga //
T02D2419:36b-7: gcig dang mi 'brel ngo mtshar che //
T02D2419:36b-8: mya ngan 'das pa'i gnas su ni //
T02D2419:36b-9: me tog ldum ra rgyas par byed //
T02D2419:36b-10: de ni ge sar 'jib par byed //
T02D2419:36b-11: bdag nyid bo la kakko la'i //
T02D2419:36b-12: rnal 'byor rgyal po grub pa thob //
T02D2419:36b-13: lta spyod skye med kyi sgom pa zhes bya ba
